  "description": "I spotted the bird on the 16th and it has been re-found over and over for a week and a half.\u00a0 Gray bird with a darker gray back with the very light gray vertical streaks.\u00a0 The head is mostly black with the very creamy yellow head strip on top and more buffy white/yellow horizontal stripes on each cheeks.\u00a0 Thick black bill.\u00a0 Yellow plume feathers coming out from the back of the head to about half way down the back.\u00a0 Bright orange legs with a bit of black on them.\u00a0 Red eye ring around a large black pupil.",
